    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Clathria (Axosuberites) hillenburgi n. sp. (UFPEPOR 1975). A, preserved specimen; B, cross section showing the ectosome and choanosome. Scale bars: A = 2.5 cm; B = 500 μm." ;
